text:
Hi everyone!

BcnEng community hopes all of you are finding some peace and energy these days. We know how hard they can be due to the COVID-19 pandemic. We wonder how the pandemic and the current economic situation are impacting the IT community, both at the work or business level but also psychologically and well-living.

For that reason, BcnEng has created the following survey <https://forms.gle/2YBhaeKDs2EWaZn18> .

We hope all of you can help us, both by answering the survey and by sharing it with the community.

We would like to thanks <@UEDFE7J07> for all the effort she put into the form creation and <@U010PQJBJB0> who reviewed it from the legal point of view.

Cheers!

attachments.title: Impact of the COVID-19 pandemic in the IT community
attachments.text: Hi everyone! BcnEng community hopes all of you are finding some peace and energy these days. We know how hard they can be due to the COVID-19 pandemic. Before you decide whether to participate in this survey or not, we want to explain the reason behind doing this and how your information will be used. Why are we doing this? We wonder how the pandemic and the current economic situation are impacting the IT community, both at the work or business level but also psychologically and well-living. How to participate? If you want to help, click "Yes" on the "My participation in this survey is completely voluntary" checkbox. Then just answer the survey. Please provide real information when doing it, otherwise, the survey results are likely to mislead. Remember that you can drop the survey at any moment. How data is gonna be treated? All the data collected is anonymous, confidential, and secured. Data will be collected using Google Form and processed later to compile statistics that will be eventually shared publicly. Thanks a lot. Please share this survey with people around the IT community. This survey and their results are under CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/>
